data.description:
CALLING ALL INVESTORS AND FLIPPERS! Welcome to 1408 Overhill Road, your prime investment opportunity in Southwest Columbia! This fixer-upper boasts abundant potential with its expansive 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and generous 3,050 sqft. Nestled in a sought-after location, this property offers the best of both worlds- proximity to the university and the vibrant downtown scene. Situated on a desirable corner lot, this residence backs into trees and the patio is enclosed by a privacy fence. Whether you are envisioning a cozy family home or a lucrative investment venture, this property offers the perfect canvas to fulfill all your dreams!

Roof was partially replaced in 2011. Deck was replaced in 2017, All windows were replaced in 2020

Home is being sold AS-IS
